      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t您这历史知识不太行啊，<br/>\n<br/>\n15岁的Anteo Zamboni，暗杀Mussolini，当场被砍死，<br/>\n<br/>\n当年15岁的人长得比较慢，不过民主国家一般会监禁，独裁国家基本上就12岁苏共政治局签署枪毙令<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTcxNTE3NmUwZTA5ZDY3ZTc1MTVmLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xNTAwJmhlaWdodD0xMDAw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a715176e0e09d67e7515f.jpg?width=1500&amp;height=1000\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a715176e0e09d67e7515f.jpg?width=1500&amp;height=1000\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a715176e0e09d67e7515f.jpg?width=1500&amp;height=1000\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjUwYmM4YWNiNTY4Y2IzY2RiNjZlLmpwZz93aWR0aD0yNDAmaGVpZ2h0PTM1NQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f50bc8acb568cb3cdb66e.jpg?width=240&amp;height=355\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f50bc8acb568cb3cdb66e.jpg?width=240&amp;height=355\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f50bc8acb568cb3cdb66e.jpg?width=240&amp;height=355\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvN2YwNWE5OTlmODIyZjFjY2YzOGVkLmpwZz93aWR0aD00NDAmaGVpZ2h0PTM0MQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7f05a999f822f1ccf38ed.jpg?width=440&amp;height=341\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7f05a999f822f1ccf38ed.jpg?width=440&amp;height=341\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7f05a999f822f1ccf38ed.jpg?width=440&amp;height=341\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMTFhYWExMmFmNzRkOGI0NmQzZTc4LmpwZz93aWR0aD00NDAmaGVpZ2h0PTU1Ng\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/11aaa12af74d8b46d3e78.jpg?width=440&amp;height=556\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/11aaa